data.description: Location, location, location!!  This masterfully updated 3 bedroom, 2 bath ranch over a full finished basement has best of all worlds sitting in the quiet serenity of 3 wooded acres, yet to close to everything.  It's perfectly placed minutes from downtown Acworth, downtown Cartersville, Lakepoint sports, and I-75.  Walk through the front door and you'll immediately feel at home in the cozy yet elegantly designed spaces.  The open concept living, dining and kitchen are beautifully accented by the wood beamed ceilings and large, brick real wood fireplace.  The bright open kitchen boasts brand new appliances and cabinets galore.  The sunroom in the back is a great place to watch the wildlife and the oversized master bedroom is quietly tucked away - perfect for getting rest and rejuvenation.  Head down to the full, finished basement for game night. Whether you're playing or watching them - there's plenty of room for both!  Don't wait, this one won't last- schedule your showing today!
